title: Exploring the Trade Candidates That Could Shuffle the League | The Corner 3 (Ep. 354)
description:
The Kings are our kings and we hope the trade market might heat up soon for guys like Kevin Love and Tim Hardaway Jr.. Plus, we throw an outlet pass to the games we’re looking forward to this weekend.

Hosts: Kevin O’Connor, Jonathan Tjarks, Danny Chau
